      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *
      ** +--------------------------------------+
      ** ¦ Manually included D-specs            ¦
      ** ¦ =========================            ¦
      ** +--------------------------------------+
      *
      ** +--------------------------------------+
      ** ¦ Named constants                      ¦
      ** ¦ ===============                      ¦
      ** +--------------------------------------+
      *
      ** +--------------------------------------+
      ** ¦ Arrays and Data Structures           ¦
      ** ¦ ==========================           ¦
      ** +--------------------------------------+
      *
      ** Securities screen 2 details from incoming transaction
      ** - screen format
     D NwSE2ScnFmt   E DS                  EXTNAME(SESEC2PD)
      *
      ** Securities for file update - file format
     D NwSEFilFmt    E DS                  EXTNAME(SEVSECSPD)
      *
      ** Securities screen 2 error indicators
     D SEESEC2       E DS                  EXTNAME(SEESEC2PD)
      *
      ** DS to hold coupon/rate days array
     D SCD             S              4A   DIM(12)
      *
      ** +--------------------------------------+
      ** ¦ Declared variables                   ¦
      ** ¦ ==================                   ¦
      ** +--------------------------------------+
      *
      ** Index for arrays of error message ids, etc.
     D IDx             S              3P 0
      *
      ** Parameters for ZALIGN
     D ZAlignOK        S              1A
     D ZField          S             16A
     D ZADec           S              1P 0
     D ZADig           S              2P 0
      *
      ** Work variables
     D WCmFq           S              2P 0
     D Wx              S              2P 0
      *
      ** +--------------------------------------+
      ** ¦ End of D-specs                       ¦
      ** ¦ ==============                       ¦
      ** +--------------------------------------+
      *
      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *
      ** +--- Start of Main processing -------------------------------+
      ** ¦                                                            ¦
      ** ¦ *INZSR is executed at program activation.                  ¦
      ** ¦                                                            ¦
      ** +------------------------------------------------------------+
      *
      ** Initialise work variables.
     C                   EVAL      IDx = 0
     C                   EVAL      WCmFq = 0

     C                   MOVE      DDCD01        SCD(1)
     C                   MOVE      DDCD02        SCD(2)
     C                   MOVE      DDCD03        SCD(3)
     C                   MOVE      DDCD04        SCD(4)
     C                   MOVE      DDCD05        SCD(5)
     C                   MOVE      DDCD06        SCD(6)
     C                   MOVE      DDCD07        SCD(7)
     C                   MOVE      DDCD08        SCD(8)
     C                   MOVE      DDCD09        SCD(9)
     C                   MOVE      DDCD10        SCD(10)
     C                   MOVE      DDCD11        SCD(11)
     C                   MOVE      DDCD12        SCD(12)
      *
      ** Validate compounding frequency
      *
     C                   EXSR      SRValCMFrq
      *
      ** If an error has been found, set return code appropriately.
      ** Otherwise, update valid file fields.
      *
     C                   IF        OKCMFQ = 'N'
     C                   EVAL      RetCodeIn = 'ERROR'
     C                   ENDIF

     C                   IF        OKCMFQ <> 'N'
     C                   Z-ADD     WCmFq         S1CMFQ
     C                   ENDIF

     C                   RETURN
      *
      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRVALCMFRQ - Validation for Compounding Frequency            *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
     C     SRValCMFrq    BEGSR
      *                                                                                       209294
     C                   IF        DDCMFQ = '00'                                              209294
     C                   MOVE      *BLANKS       DDCMFQ                                       209294
     C                   ENDIF                                                                209294
      *
      ** If blank, default compounding frequebcy to no. of coupons
      ** per year.
      *
     C                   IF        DDCMFQ = *BLANKS
     C                   Z-ADD     0             Wx

     C     Wx            DOWLT     12
     C                   ADD       1             Wx

     C                   IF        SCD(Wx) = *BLANKS
     C     Wx            SUB       1             WCmFq
     C                   MOVE      WCmFq         DDCMFQ
     C                   Z-ADD     13            Wx
     C                   ENDIF

     C                   ENDDO

     C                   IF        Wx = 12 AND
     C                             SCD(Wx) <> *BLANKS
     C                   MOVE      12            DDCMFQ
     C                   ENDIF

     C                   ELSE

     C                   MOVE      *BLANKS       ZField
     C                   MOVE      DDCMFQ        ZField
     C                   Z-ADD     2             ZADig
     C                   Z-ADD     0             ZADec

     C                   CALLB     'ZALIGN'
     C                   PARM                    ZAlignOK
     C                   PARM                    ZField
     C                   PARM                    ZADec
     C                   PARM                    ZADig

     C                   IF        ZAlignOk = 'Y'
     C                   MOVE      ZField        WCmFq
     C                   ENDIF

     C                   IF        ZAlignOk <> 'Y' OR
     C                             WCmFq < 1 OR WCmFq > 12
     C**********         MOVE      'N'           OKSYBS                                       206957
     C                   EVAL      OKCMFQ = 'N'                                               206957
     C                   ADD       1             IDx
     C                   MOVEL     'DDSYBS'      FldNamXAr(IDx)
     C                   MOVEL     'SEA0219'     MsgIdXAr(IDx)
     C                   ENDIF

     C                   ENDIF

     C                   ENDSR
      *
      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  *INZSR - Program Initialisation                              *
      *         - This subroutine runs automatically for program      *
      *           initialisation.                                     *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
